      "role": "user",
      "content": "so if the main issue is that these benefits are making people opt out of the workforce, doesn't that mean the expansion of these programs is actually hurting the economy in the long run by shrinking the talent pool? it seems like a pretty clear-cut case where more spending leads to less productivity.",
